00:01:58.250 --> 00:01:59.685
&gt;&gt; [LAUGH]
&gt;&gt; Sort of like the dancing thing.

00:01:59.685 --> 00:02:00.555
&gt;&gt; Yeah, [LAUGH] exactly.

